<style>
  .foundation-section {
    /* height: 100vh; */
    width: 100%;
    background-color: var(--dark-900);
  }

  .foundation-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    column-gap: 2em;
  }

  .foundation-section_title {
    grid-row: 1;
    grid-column: 1;
  }

  .foundation-title_span {
    color: var(--accent-500);
  }

  .foundation-section_text {
    grid-row: 2;
    grid-column: 1;
  }
  .foundation-section_outro {
    grid-row: 3;
    grid-column: 1;
  }

  .radial-container {
    grid-row: 1 / span 3;
    grid-column: 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2em;
    margin-top: 4em;
  }

  /*  RADIAL STUFF */
  .radial {
    position: relative;
    /* Size is driven by the --size variable */
    --size: min(420px, 80vw);
    --r: calc(var(--size) * 0.38); /* radius = 38% of total size */
    width: var(--size);
    height: var(--size);
  }

  .hub {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: calc(var(--size) * 0.155);
    height: calc(var(--size) * 0.155);
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-muted);
    background: rgba(141, 229, 228, 0.04);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2px;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hub-label {
    font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace;
    font-size: calc(var(--size) * 0.022);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hub-dot {
    width: calc(var(--size) * 0.014);
    height: calc(var(--size) * 0.014);
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(141, 229, 228, 0.75);
    margin-top: 3px;
  }

  .node {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: calc(var(--size) * 0.022);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .node-dot {
    width: calc(var(--size) * 0.03);
    height: calc(var(--size) * 0.03);
    min-width: 10px;
    min-height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-500);
    background: rgba(141, 229, 228, 0.08);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .node-dot::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 40%;
    height: 40%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-500);
  }

  .node-label {
    font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace;
    font-size: calc(var(--size) * 0.026);
    font-size: clamp(8px, calc(var(--size) * 0.026), 11px);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .nodes {
    list-style: none;
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    /* inherits --size and --r from .radial */
  }

  /* ── Node positions ──
   Hexagon: 6 points at 60° intervals
   Angles: 270°(top), 330°, 30°, 90°(bottom), 150°, 210°
   x = cos(angle) * r,  y = sin(angle) * r
   270° → x=0,      y=-r
   330° → x=0.866r, y=-0.5r
    30° → x=0.866r, y=0.5r
    90° → x=0,      y=r
   150° → x=-0.866r,y=0.5r
   210° → x=-0.866r,y=-0.5r
── */

  /* top */
  .node-1 {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translate(0, calc(var(--r) * -1));
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .node-1 .node-dot {
    order: 2;
  }
  .node-1 .node-label {
    order: 1;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--size) * 0.018);
  }

  /* top-right */
  .node-2 {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
      translate(calc(var(--r) * 0.866), calc(var(--r) * -0.5));
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  /* bottom-right */
  .node-3 {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
      translate(calc(var(--r) * 0.866), calc(var(--r) * 0.5));
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  /* bottom */
  .node-4 {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translate(0, var(--r));
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .node-4 .node-label {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: calc(var(--size) * 0.018);
  }

  /* bottom-left */
  .node-5 {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
      translate(calc(var(--r) * -0.866), calc(var(--r) * 0.5));
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }
  .node-5 .node-label {
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* top-left */
  .node-6 {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
      translate(calc(var(--r) * -0.866), calc(var(--r) * -0.5));
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }
  .node-6 .node-label {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .node-label {
    /* max-width: 50px; */
  }
  /* Tablet: narrow left column */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .tech-body {
      grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    }
    .radial {
      --size: min(380px, 70vw);
    }
  }

  /* Mobile: stack vertically */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .tech-body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .radial {
      --size: min(340px, 85vw);
    }
    /* On mobile, labels can wrap */
    .node-label {
      white-space: normal;
      max-width: 90px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 776px) {
    .foundation-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2em;
    }

    .radial-container {
      grid-row: 3;
      grid-column: 1;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .foundation-section_text {
      grid-row: 4;
    }

    .foundation-section_outro {
      grid-row: 5;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="foundation-section">
  <section class="foundation-inner inner-container">
    <h2 class="section-title foundation-section_title">
      Technology <span class="section-title_span foundation-title_span"
        >Foundation</span
      >
    </h2>
    <p class="section-text foundation-section_text">
      Our technical direction is based on the idea that light can be structured,
      directed, and potentially used functionally within three-dimensional
      holographic forms, rather than relying solely on conventional metallic
      wiring.
    </p>
    <p class="section-text text-muted foundation-section_outro">
      This work has been shaped through several years of internal research and
      concept development, supported by related experience in holographic
      systems, optical design, neural-network thinking, and applied AI.
    </p>

    <div class="radial-container">
      <p class="radial-title text-muted">
        The platform brings together several areas of technical thinking,
        including:
      </p>
      <div class="radial">
        <div class="hub">
          <span class="hub-label">AGI<br />∞</span>
          <div class="hub-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <ul class="nodes">
          <li class="node node-1">
            <div class="node-dot"></div>
            <div class="node-label">
              Computer-generated<br />holography
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="node node-2">
            <div class="node-dot"></div>
            <div class="node-label">
              Nano-optical<br />design
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="node node-3">
            <div class="node-dot"></div>
            <div class="node-label">
              Volumetric optical<br />pathways
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="node node-4">
            <div class="node-dot"></div>
            <div class="node-label">Metamaterial hybrid-based</div>
          </li>

          <li class="node node-5">
            <div class="node-dot"></div>
            <div class="node-label">
              Logic and switching <br />concepts
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="node node-6">
            <div class="node-dot"></div>
            <div class="node-label">
              AI-related control <br />concepts
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
